<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/895156-i-loved-the-bear-and-the-nightingale-is">I loved The Bear and the Nightingale. Is there any chance you will write a sequel? I would especially like to know more about Sasha!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_895156'><a id="like_count_community_question_895156" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/895156?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">81 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25489134-the-bear-and-the-nightingale">like</a></span>

